rows.label: qev050203_MSG0001
rows.name: N-no. This is not possible. I LOST?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050203_MSG0002
rows.name:
YOU! Who are you?! You fight with the strength of my
brothers, and perhaps more.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050203_SEL0011
rows.name:
Bluntly tell Zo Zazhi that her lack of
skill will end up getting her killed.

rows.label: qev050203_SEL0021
rows.name:
Gently tell Zo Zazhi that her brothers
would not want her to die.

rows.label: qev050203_MSG0003
rows.name: Rrgh! And you claim this battle proves so?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050203_MSG0005
rows.name:
No. You speak the truth. At my present level of skill,
I could not hope to defeat the one who cut down my
brothers.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050203_MSG0006
rows.name: Damn... DAMN! Is that really the truth of it?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050203_MSG0007
rows.name: But I will not give up. I cannot.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050203_MSG0008
rows.name:
I shall train and grow strong enough to crush him
AND you![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050203_MSG0009
rows.name:
I will return home for now, human.
But one day, vengeance will be mine![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050203_MSG0010
rows.name:
And not just upon him. I will carve all of the Ganglion
limb from limb![ST:wait ]
